    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>DeadEye</strong> 是一款节奏紧张、动作爽快的 <strong>2D 像素风 Roguelike 射击游戏</strong>，故事发生在一个被禁忌契约与黑暗秘密所吞噬的世界中。<br>你将扮演 <strong>Douglas</strong> 或 <strong>Blood Samurai</strong>，两位与神秘契约 <strong>DeadEye</strong> 相连的英雄。该契约赋予你 <strong>停止时间</strong> 的能力，让你在瞬间连锁释放致命行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每一秒都至关重要。你必须充分利用时间，才能在无尽的怪物浪潮中生存下来，完成任务，击败残忍无情的首领——包括守护诅咒墓地的强大巫妖 <strong>Lorian</strong>——并逐步揭开 DeadEye 背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/ba29a405575ee024f0b2964dd1c3f2aa.avif?t=1770393051\" width=261 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">掌控时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/825463c56262197b99daf20b5ee30f35.poster.avif?t=1770393051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/825463c56262197b99daf20b5ee30f35.webm?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/825463c56262197b99daf20b5ee30f35.mp4?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">激活 DeadEye，可短暂冻结整个战场。<br>在时间停滞的瞬间，提前规划射击、装填与移动路线，随后释放一场毁灭性的行动风暴。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">左轮手枪与连击系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/439a78197259c01c13997e63e025c495.poster.avif?t=1770393051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/439a78197259c01c13997e63e025c495.webm?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/439a78197259c01c13997e63e025c495.mp4?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">使用一把 <strong>六发装填的左轮手枪</strong> 进行战斗。<br>精准射击与恰当装填可维持连击数，连击将大幅提升 <strong>伤害、经验值与金币获取量</strong>。<br>一旦连击中断，你的成长节奏也将被放缓。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">无尽波次与动态任务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/be8bfa5e875b4642488f082d25ed41fb.poster.avif?t=1770393051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/be8bfa5e875b4642488f082d25ed41fb.webm?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/be8bfa5e875b4642488f082d25ed41fb.mp4?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">迎战源源不断的敌人浪潮，每一局游戏都会随机生成 <strong>可选任务</strong>。<br>完成目标即可获得奖励，并挑战越来越强大的首领敌人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">93 种神器与强化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/0f3c782f83fff4f10d2387a5a05baf1d.poster.avif?t=1770393051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/0f3c782f83fff4f10d2387a5a05baf1d.webm?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/0f3c782f83fff4f10d2387a5a05baf1d.mp4?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">解锁并组合 <strong>93 种不同稀有度的神器</strong>。<br>其中包含高风险高回报的 <strong>诅咒神器</strong>，它们能提供巨大力量，但会附带负面效果。<br>从 <strong>11 种核心属性</strong> 中进行选择（暴击、契约强化、状态效果、子弹效果等），打造属于你的独特流派。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">契约系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/5c375cec5b779964b869884a6885ee7b.poster.avif?t=1770393051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/5c375cec5b779964b869884a6885ee7b.webm?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/5c375cec5b779964b869884a6885ee7b.mp4?t=1770393051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从 <strong>6 种契约</strong> 中选择其一，并将其进化为 <strong>进攻型、防御型、全能型或中立型</strong>。<br>每一次选择，都会从根本上改变你的战斗策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">角色与宠物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/68f89f611ddf77883bd173b3bc244a88.avif?t=1770393051\" width=1108 height=618 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">选择 Douglas 或 Blood Samurai 进行游戏，并通过 <strong>可装备符文的独特宠物</strong> 强化你的成长路线。<br>宠物等级越高，提供的增益效果越强——合理利用这一系统，将让你变得无比强大。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">成就与长期成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/1d258c5b1a61f7f1befd3859df5bee2a.avif?t=1770393051\" width=1108 height=622 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">解锁 <strong>45 项成就</strong>，并与 Steam 平台完全整合，记录你的每一次突破。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">语言与无障碍支持</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">支持 <strong>10 种语言</strong>，提供可自定义操作方式与触控友好界面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Douglas 的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/ca17e79c7191ca0554ffc04ceba5ce14.avif?t=1770393051\" width=684 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在与某个神秘存在缔结契约之后，Douglas 获得了操纵时间、连锁释放致命行动的力量。<br>然而，即便拥有如此强大的能力，他的内心却始终无法平静。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">他的灵魂早已感到沉重而空虚，而直觉不断告诉他——<br><strong>答案，就藏在 DeadEye 之中。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">为了找回失去的一切，并弄清楚这份力量真正付出的代价，Douglas 踏上了一段穿越敌意世界、追寻真相的危险旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312890/extras/139449085d7642c836bdc6c8bd3aeadb.avif?t=1770393051\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p>",
